title: Definitions
context: J. Rental Housing Revolving Fund Note Subpart heading amended by L 2015, c 237, ยง23. ยง201H-201 Definitions. As used in this subpart, unless a different meaning is clearly required by the context: &ldquo;Develop&rdquo; or &ldquo;development&rdquo; means the planning, financing, or acquisition of real and personal property; demolition of existing structures; clearance of real property; construction, reconstruction, alteration, or repairing of approaches, streets, sidewalks, utilities, and services, or other site improvements; construction, reconstruction, repair, remodeling, extension, equipment, or furnishing of buildings or other structures; or any combination of the foregoing, of any housing project. It also includes any undertakings necessary therefor, and the acquisition of any housing, in whole or in part. &ldquo;Fund&rdquo; means the rental housing revolving fund established pursuant to section 201H-202.
